1. __Best Effort__ - Not Strict. (FiFo) First come first serve traffic management.

<br>

2. __DiffServ__ - Less Strict. Bandwidth Guarantee for each application and share bandwidth with other apps depending on when they need it.

<br>

3. __IntServ__ - Strict. Bandwidth Guarantee for each app but does not share with other apps even if a certain app is not using bandwidth.


