## Policing

### 🎯 Exercise 13: Prevent ICMP Overload

~~~
!@UTM-PH
config t
 no ip access-list extended PING
 ip access-list extended PING
  permit icmp any any
  !
 class-map CM-PING
  match access-group name PING
  !
 no policy-map PM-PING
 policy-map PM-PING
  class CM-PING
   police 8000 conform-action transmit exceed-action drop
   exit
  exit
 !
 control-plane
  service-policy input PM-PING
  exit
do sh policy-map control-plane
~~~


