### 🎯 Exercise 15: Configure CoPP  that will block HTTP & HTTPS Traffic but allow TELNET and SSH traffic using only one service-policy.
Make sure the following parameters are set to prevent HTTP & HTTPS Traffic:
- Rate: 80_000
- Burst: 1500
- Burst_Max: 1500

~~~
!@UTM-PH
conf t
 access-list 101 deny tcp any any eq 443
 access-list 101 permit ip any any
 !
 class-map match-all WEB
   match access-group 101
 !
 no policy-map Control-Plane-Policing
 policy-map WEB-COPP
  class WEB
    police 80000 1500 1500 conform-action transmit exceed-action drop violate-action drop
    exit
  exit
 !
 control-plane
  service-policy input Control-Plane-Policing
  end
~~~
